\c 130
\s Munyengetero wekukumbira kanganwiro nekununurwa
\d Rwiyo rwekukwira.
\p
\v 1 Ndiri muudziku ndakadanidzira kwamuri, Jehovha.
\v 2 Ishe, inzwai inzwi rangu; nzeve dzenyu ngadziteerere inzwi remikumbiro yangu.
\v 3 Dai imwi Jehovha, maicherekedza zvitadzo, Ishe, ndiani angamira?
\v 4 Asi kwamuri kune kanganwiro, kuti mutyiwe.
\p
\v 5 Ndakamirira Jehovha; mweya weupenyu wangu unomirira; uye ndinotaririra shoko rake.
\v 6 Mweya weupenyu wangu \add unorindira\add* Ishe, kupfuura vanorindira rungwanani, vakarindira rungwanani.
\p
\v 7 Israeri ngaataririre kuna Jehovha, nokuti kuna Jehovha kune tsitsi, uye kwaari kune rudzikinuro rukuru.
\v 8 Zvino iye anodzikinura Israeri pazvitadzo zvake zvose.